[h1]逻辑网络[/h1]
[h1][i]Logic Network[/i][/h1]

提供独立的可编程自动化信号输出器。通过浏览器中的节点编辑器组合数学、比较、布尔和时序逻辑，输出单通道或四通道自动化信号。

[i]Logic Network is a standalone programmable automation signal emitter. Compose math, comparison, boolean, and timing logic in a browser-based node editor, then output single-channel or four-channel automation signals.[/i]

[h2]主要功能 / Main Features[/h2]
[list]
[*] 节点式逻辑编辑器，支持数学、比较、布尔、时序和信号变换模块。
[*] [i]Node-based logic editor with math, comparison, boolean, timing, and signal transformation modules.[/i]
[*] 单通道和四通道自动化输出。
[*] [i]Single-channel and four-channel automation output.[/i]
[*] 自动保存当前存档中的配置。
[*] [i]Per-save configuration persistence for the Logic Network signal emitter.[/i]
[/list]
